'''Free League Publishing''' is a Swedish-based publisher and game creator company, founded in [[2011]].
Since 2015, the company has published role-playing games from a list of licensed and home-grown properties. On February 11, 2021, the company launched a Kickstarter campaign for the publishing of a second edition of [[The One Ring (role-playing game)|''The One Ring'']], of which was later delivered to supporters at the beginning of October of the same year.<ref name=TOR2posts>[https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1192053011/the-one-ring-roleplaying-game-second-edition/posts Kickstarter Updates]</ref> The game was subsequently released for retail purchase, on the [[22 March|22nd of March]] [[2022]].<ref name=TOR2R1>[https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1192053011/the-one-ring-roleplaying-game-second-edition/posts/3460049 Kickstarter Update: Retail Release]</ref><ref name=TOR2R2>[https://us3.campaign-archive.com/?u=2dcfb24fb7c8d0fb9c2f52040&id=2354eca464 "The One Ring™ RPG Out Now!"]</ref>
On the [[29 May|29th of May]] [[2023]], Free League released [[The Lord of the Rings Roleplaying]] game.<ref name=LOTR5E>[https://us3.campaign-archive.com/?u=2dcfb24fb7c8d0fb9c2f52040&id=bec69bcc9e The Lord of the Rings™ Roleplaying Out]</ref>
